26:53.000 --> 26:58.000
which now is called naive set theory, doesn't work out.

26:58.000 --> 27:01.000
So what do we do?

27:01.000 --> 27:05.000
Well, there are various ways of trying to respond to this paradox.

27:05.000 --> 27:10.000
And they were really the chief obsession of mathematical logicians

27:10.000 --> 27:13.000
